divs: Sighting DetailsOutside at night looking at the full moon on May5th 2012 @ 9:45pm and 5 orange objects come across the sky out of the SW direction travelling NE First one comes across at approxamtely 9:50pm and seems to be travelling about 200 miles per hour and a minute later another one comes by and the another 3 come by about a minute apart from each other Strange
Summary: 5 round red/orange glowing objects following in each other rather quickly about 30to 60 seconds apart, traveling north, no sound at all.
